00:56:29.804 --> 00:56:32.775
It's us grown-ups who really need compliments.

802
00:56:36.574 --> 00:56:38.244
Good job, Mr. Han.

803
00:56:42.585 --> 00:56:46.784
(Good job!)

804
00:56:57.295 --> 00:56:58.295
Don't cry.

805
00:56:58.994 --> 00:57:00.634
My heart ached...

806
00:57:02.005 --> 00:57:03.935
when I saw you cry...

807
00:57:05.875 --> 00:57:07.235
like a little child.

808
00:57:15.985 --> 00:57:18.154
And to be honest, when we first met,

809
00:57:20.384 --> 00:57:22.424
I was determined not to fall in love again,

810
00:57:25.755 --> 00:57:27.554
but you totally made me forget about that.

811
00:58:28.185 --> 00:58:29.654
Just like you,

812
00:58:30.755 --> 00:58:32.455
I also want to be happy.

813
00:58:33.795 --> 00:58:35.424
And just like you,

814
00:58:36.065 --> 00:58:37.725
I want to be honest about how I feel.

815
00:59:00.614 --> 00:59:02.384
But I've been through enough to know...

816
00:59:05.025 --> 00:59:06.694
that it's not just me who ends up getting hurt.

817
00:59:10.295 --> 00:59:11.694
The other person gets hurt as well.

818
00:59:20.435 --> 00:59:22.074
You may have entered my heart...

819
00:59:23.304 --> 00:59:25.174
and stirred me up like this.

820
00:59:28.114 --> 00:59:29.614
But all I need to do is just ignore it.

821
00:59:56.005 --> 00:59:57.105
I just need to make sure...

822
00:59:58.815 --> 01:00:00.275
my heart doesn't flutter again.

823
01:00:47.295 --> 01:00:48.824
Why do we keep running into each other?

824
01:00:51.565 --> 01:00:52.594
Why do you keep...

825
01:00:54.835 --> 01:00:56.335
showing up like this?

826
01:01:00.134 --> 01:01:01.275
It truly is a coincidence.

827
01:01:03.174 --> 01:01:04.275
Good night, then.

828
01:01:29.634 --> 01:01:30.735
How can...

829
01:01:33.705 --> 01:01:35.904
you be this beautiful?

830
01:01:40.475 --> 01:01:41.844
And what if I'm beautiful?

831
01:01:47.884 --> 01:01:48.985
What comes next?

832
01:03:32.324 --> 01:03:34.994
(Oh My Baby)

833
01:03:34.994 --> 01:03:37.464
Is your pregnancy project...

834
01:03:37.464 --> 01:03:39.034
finally over then?

835
01:03:39.034 --> 01:03:42.404
Don't you think it's too soon to mention that after day one?

836
01:03:43.034 --> 01:03:44.634
Ms. Jang, can I see your hand?

837
01:03:45.475 --> 01:03:47.605
- Ta-da! - What are you doing?

838
01:03:47.634 --> 01:03:50.375
I don't like that you're dating him!

839
01:03:50.574 --> 01:03:52.174
I waited 10 years for a love like this.

840
01:03:52.375 --> 01:03:55.344
Ha Ri won't see you again if she knows what you're up to.

841
01:03:55.614 --> 01:03:58.955
There's something I wanted to share with you.

842
01:03:59.255 --> 01:04:01.985
But I don't think I can give it to you.

